Use Case 1: Loyalty Status SMS Notification

Cumulus Bank and Financial Services want to send an SMS message to customers who have earned a new loyalty status.

Let's review the solution steps for this campaign.

Establish Campaign Requirements
Identify campaign goals
Send an SMS notification when a customer’s reward status has changed.
The campaign is ongoing, regularly adding customers who meet the criteria.
Identify personalization components
SMS includes the customer’s first name and their previous and new loyalty status.
Identity audience and data sources
Active customers whose loyalty level has changed in the past 7 days.
Unified Individual, Loyalty Program Member, and Loyalty Member Tier data sources.
Gather campaign materials
Compose the copy for the SMS message in Marketing Cloud Engagement.
